[{"id":"VR834508","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows four identically charged spheres arranged along line. The three spheres to the left are a distance of D apart. The fourth sphere is further to the right, and point P is indicated a distance of D between the third and fourth spheres.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR834508.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Four small, identical charged spheres, each of charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive Q\"><math alttext=\"positive Q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>+</mo><mi>Q</mi></mpadded></math></span></span>, are located along a line near Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure. What is the electric potential at Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>P</mtext></math></span></span> due to the four spheres?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR834508_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 2 times the fraction k Q over D\"><math alttext=\"positive 2 times the fraction k Q over D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mi>D</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 4 times the fraction k Q over D\"><math alttext=\"positive 4 times the fraction k Q over D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mi>D</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive five sixths times the fraction k Q over D\"><math alttext=\"positive five sixths times the fraction k Q over D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mi>D</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the positive fraction 17 over 6, end fraction, times the fraction k Q over D\"><math alttext=\"the positive fraction 17 over 6, end fraction, times the fraction k Q over D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mi>D</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":3}]